column14: As a user, I want to borrow book that I want and return books after I've done reading
As a user, I want to login to an account to manage user profile, check books I've borrow so that I can return the book the before due date
As a staff, I want to be able to edit book details such the ISBN, book name, author and publish date because some of the book details were entered wrongly by other staff.
As a manager of a library, I want to check the book list and find out what books are not in the list so that I can buy and add in to the list
As a staff of a library, I want to check the number of days of the late returns to calculate the total fine for late returns.
